            <title>[PIG-692] when running script file, automatically set up job name based on the file name</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-692</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When running pig script from command like like this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;pig scriptfile&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;right now default job name is used. it is convenient to have it automatically set up based on the script name.&lt;/p&gt;
